ole for a smooth and energized ride',1,'2019-06-16 17:04:02','2019-06-20 17:12:54',0,2,0,2),(29,'ASWEEGO SHOES CLOUD WHITE / CLOUD WHITE / CORE BLACK',1700000,'ASWEEGO SHOES\r\nRUNNING SHOES THAT FLEX FOR A SMOOTH, ADAPTABLE RIDE.\r\nShoes with flexibility and responsiveness for multisport training. These shoes have a knit textile upper that hugs the foot for a sock-like fit. Pillow-like midsole cushioning provides long-lasting comfort. Durable rubber inserts at the forefoot and heel provide added grip so you\'re ready for unexpected terrain.',1,'2019-06-16 17:07:42','2019-06-20 17:12:54',0,2,0,2),(30,'ULTRABOOST 19 PRIDE SHOES COLOR: RUNNING WHITE / SCARLET / BRIGHT YELLOW',3800000,'ULTRABOOST 19 PRIDE SHOES\r\nCelebrate the beauty in diversity. These running shoes have a seamless, stretchy knit upper that adapts to the shape of your foot as you move. A flexible outsole works with dual-density cushioning for endless energy and a smooth stride',1,'2019-06-16 17:13:32','2019-06-20 17:12:54',0,2,1,2),(31,'ULTRABOOST 19 SHOES CORE BLACK / GREY SIX / GREY FOUR',3800000,'ULTRABOOST 19 SHOES\r\nSHOES WITH ENDLESS ENERGY TO REINVENT YOUR RUNNING EXPERIENCE.\r\nRunning reinvented. These high-performance neutral running shoes deliver unrivaled comfort and energy return. The lightweight and propulsive shoes have a seamless knit upper that\'s engineered with motion weave technology to provide stretch while also holding your foot in place while you run. The second-skin fit follows the shape of your foot to reduce pressure points.',1,'2019-06-16 17:15:35','2019-06-20 17:12:54',0,2,1,2),(33,'SOLAR GLIDE SHOES RAW WHITE / ACTIVE BLUE / SHOCK RED',2200000,'ULTRABOOST X MISSONI SHOES\r\nRESPONSIVE RUNNING SHOES CREATED IN COLLABORATION WITH MISSONI.\r\nBuilt for performance and comfort, these neutral running shoes give you the feeling of your best-ever run every time you lace them up. They have a lightweight knit upper that adapts to the changing shape of your foot as you run. Responsive cushioning works with the flexible outsole for a smooth and energized ride. ',1,'2019-06-16 17:20:53','2019-06-20 17:12:54',0,2,1,2),(34,'ULTRABOOST LACELESS SHOES COLOR: CLOUD WHITE / CLOUD WHITE / ACTIVE GREEN',4000000,'ULTRABOOST LACELESS SHOES\r\nLACE-FREE SHOES FOR ENERGIZED CITY RUNNING.\r\nThese neutral running shoes were designed using motion capture technology to deliver an unrestricted feel. The laceless shoes have a stretchy knit upper that hugs the foot. A forged band at the midfoot provides a supportive fit. Responsive cushioning and a flexible outsole give you a smooth ride. \r\n\r\nEngineered fit\r\nadidas Primeknit upper wraps the foot with an engineered fit for targeted support that enhances movement\r\n\r\nEndless energy\r\nBoost is our most responsive cushioning ever, delivering incredible energy return: The more energy you give, the more you get',1,'2019-06-16 17:23:35','2019-06-20 17:12:54',0,2,1,2),(35,'RAPIDARUN SHOES COLOR: ECRU TINT / GLOW PINK / ECRU TINT',1650000,'RAPIDARUN SHOES\r\nLACELESS RUNNING SHOES WITH A STANDOUT LOOK.\r\nGet ahead of the pack in these juniors\' slip-on running shoes. They\'re built with a multicolor knit textile upper that provides an adaptive fit and a standout look. A cushy midsole keeps your feet comfortable while a TPU heel clip offers ultimate stability.',1,'2019-06-16 17:26:54','2019-06-20 17:12:54',0,2,2,2),(36,'U_PATH RUN SHOES CLOUD WHITE / CLOUD WHITE / CLOUD WHITE',1200000,'U_PATH RUN SHOES\r\nMESH RUNNING-STYLE SHOES WITH A D-RING LACING SYSTEM.\r\nThe U_Path offers a sleek combination of retro and modern. These juniors\' shoes are built of soft, breathable mesh for everyday wear. The unique D-ring lacing system is inspired by a \'70s running sneaker design. A bungee heel piece adds support, and a lightweight EVA midsole provides all-day wearability.',1,'2019-06-16 17:35:38','2019-06-20 17:12:54',0,2,3,2),(37,'BASELINE SHOES CLOUD WHITE / CORE BLACK / CLOUD WHITE',1000000,'BASELINE SHOES\r\nStyle\'s starting point. These casual kids\' shoes are made with a suede upper and have simple lines for premium understated style.',1,'2019-06-16 17:37:10','2019-06-20 17:12:54',0,2,3,2),(38,'RAPIDARUN WIDE SHOES CORE BLACK / CARBON / SOLAR RED',1250000,'RAPIDARUN WIDE SHOES\r\nRUNNING SHOES WITH EXTRA ROOM WHERE YOU NEED IT.\r\nGet ready to race around the park, gym or track in these juniors\' running shoes. They\'re made of a breathable mesh upper with overlays for protection. A TPU heel clip gives you extra stability, and a cushy midsole keeps your feet comfortable all day. A wide fit provides additional room where you need it most.',1,'2019-06-16 17:38:53','2019-06-20 17:12:54',0,2,2,2),(39,'ERA COLOR-BLACK',1000000,'The Era, Vans classic low top lace-up skate shoe, has a durable double-stitched canvas upper with padded tongue and lining and Vans signature Waffle Outsole.',3,'2019-06-16 17:47:33','2019-06-19 17:59:20',0,9,0,2),(40,'OLD SKOOL BLACK/WHITE',1200000,'The Old Skool, Vans classic skate shoe and the first to bear the iconic side stripe, has a low-top lace-up silhouette with a durable suede and canvas upper with padded tongue and lining and Vans signature Waffle Outsole.',3,'2019-06-16 17:52:02','2019-06-19 17:59:32',0,9,0,2),(41,'SLIP-ON COLOR-TRUE WHITE',1000000,'The Classic Slip-On has a low profile, slip-on canvas upper with all-over checker print, elastic side accents, Vans flag label and Vans original Waffle Outsole.',3,'2019-06-16 17:58:12','2019-06-19 17:59:44',0,9,0,2),(42,'CHECKERBOARD SLIP-ON  COLOR-TRUE WHITE/TRUE WHITE',1000000,'The Checkerboard Classic Slip-On features sturdy low profile slip-on canvas uppers with the iconic Vans checkerboard print, padded collars, elastic side accents, and signature rubber waffle outsoles.',3,'2019-06-16 18:01:17','2019-06-19 17:59:55',0,9,0,2),(43,'OLD SKOOL Women COLOR-BLACK/WHITE',1200000,'The Old Skool, Vans classic skate shoe and the first to bear the iconic side stripe, has a low-top lace-up silhouette with a durable suede and canvas upper with padded tongue and lining and Vans signature Waffle Outsole.',3,'2019-06-16 18:05:37','2019-06-19 18:00:07',0,9,1,2),(44,'PLAID ERA Women COLOR-WHITE/TRUE WHITE',1200000,'The Plaid Era combines the Vans classic low top skate shoe with sturdy textile uppers, metal eyelets, padded collars for support and flexibility, and signature rubber waffle outsoles.',3,'2019-06-16 18:08:48','2019-06-19 18:00:19',0,9,1,2),(45,'VANS X HARRY POTTER SK8-HI ZIP COLOR-GRYFFINDOR/MULTI',1000000,'This season, Vans and HARRY POTTER have conjured up a magical collection for witches, wizards, and muggles alike. Featuring sturdy canvas and suede uppers, the Vans x HARRY POTTER Sk8-Hi Zip also includes padded collars for support and flexibility, signature rubber waffle outsoles, custom collaboration details, and a zipper entry at the heel.  Display your GRYFFINDOR™ loyalty in genuine “Off The Wall” style.',3,'2019-06-16 18:12:24','2019-06-19 18:00:31',0,9,2,2),(47,'KIDS CHECKERBOARD OLD SKOOL COLOR-RAINBOW/TRUE WHITE',850000,'The Checkerboard Old Skool, the Vans classic skate shoe and first to bare the iconic sidestripe, is a low top lace-up featuring sturdy suede and canvas uppers with the iconic Vans checkerboard print, re-enforced toecaps to withstand repeated wear, padded collars for support and flexibility, and signature rubber waffle outsoles.\r\n\r\nEach season we offer a range of shoes, apparel and accessories styled with rainbow motifs to enable our global consumers the ability to express their own individuality and creative expression. To celebrate Pride Month 2019, Vans is donating $50,000 to The Trevor Project, the world’s largest suicide prevention and crisis intervention organization for LGBTQ (lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender, queer and questioning) young people.',3,'2019-06-16 18:20:37','2019-06-19 18:01:05',0,9,3,2),(48,'Chuck Taylor All Star Low Top Optical White',1000000,'WE MAKE THE SHOE. YOU MAKE THE STORIES.\r\nIt started when